      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional specimen that defines 'showroom condition.' This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and shows zero signs of wear. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with a professional ceramic coating applied annually; there are absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh state. The premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the original floor mats have been protected by weather-proof overlays since day one. It has never been smoked in and retains that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. I have a comprehensive binder of every service record performed exclusively at the dealership, showing preventative maintenance well ahead of schedule. The engine bay is spotless, the transmission shifts with surgical precision, and the tires are high-performance Michelin Pilots with 90% tread remaining. This sale includes both original fobs, all factory manuals, a custom-fit car cover, and a clean title in hand. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this is the one.",
